<section>
  <div class="content-block" style="float:none">
    <h2>Benchmarking</h2>
    <p>We have benchmarked the responses so far to give an overview of how the sector is moving towards digital maturity, you can read the report <a href='https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/digitalmaturitymatrix/Third_Sector_Digital_Maturity_-_A_Benchmark.pdf'> here</a>.</p>
  </div>
