    <h2>Open source</h2>
    <p>The application is open source and built using Ruby on Rails. Feel free to <a href="https://github.com/timpwbaker/digital-maturity-matrix">submit any feature requests to github</a>, although we make this all in our own time so can't promise to be super agile on it.</p>
